author: Minecraft
description:
2025 is coming to an end, and Vu Bui is taking a trip down memory lane, remembering all the fun we’ve had in Minecraft over the past 12 months – and perhaps he even learns how to play the bugle!

It’s been a busy, fantastic, and exciting year, and we’re not sure how we managed it all, whether it’s magic, time travel, or coffee that fueled us. We’ve released four game drops featuring new mob variants, the happy ghast, more copper than ever, and all the mounts you’ll ever need! We’ve made sure people get triggered by hearing the words “chicken” and “jockey,” the Marketplace has been bubbling, and two new multiplayer adventures have been added to the Minecraft world!

And none of this would have been possible without you – the fans, players, and block-lovers! Your passion is what fuels us (not coffee)!
See you in 2026, but first, check out all this fun stuff from 2025:

• 00:00 – 00:36 – Intro time!
• 00:37 – 01:00 – 2025’s first game drop – Spring to Life!
• 01:01 – 01:15 – A look back
title: Minecraft 2025 in 5 Minutes 🎉 | MINECRAFT MONTHLY
